{"id":4397,"date":"2019-09-30T01:24:41","date_gmt":"2019-09-30T01:24:41","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/?p=4397"},"modified":"2020-02-08T21:04:53","modified_gmt":"2020-02-08T14:04:53","slug":"nhung-xu-huong-to-chuc-su-kien-moi-nhat-2019","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/nhung-xu-huong-to-chuc-su-kien-moi-nhat-2019.html\/","title":{"rendered":"Nh\u1eefng xu h\u01b0\u1edbng T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c S\u1ef1 Ki\u1ec7n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t 2020"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_36 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">N\u1ed9i Dung<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: none;\"><label for=\"item\" aria-label=\"Table of Content\"><span style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;width: 35px;height: 30px;justify-content: center;\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"item\"><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/nhung-xu-huong-to-chuc-su-kien-moi-nhat-2019.html\/#To_chuc_su_kien_ket_hop_team-building\" title=\"T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p team-building\">T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p team-building<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/nhung-xu-huong-to-chuc-su-kien-moi-nhat-2019.html\/#To_chuc_su_kien_than_thien_voi_moi_truong\" title=\"T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng\">T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/nhung-xu-huong-to-chuc-su-kien-moi-nhat-2019.html\/#Ung_dung_cong_nghe_hien_dai_vao_to_chuc_su_kien\" title=\"\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0o t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n\">\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0o t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/nhung-xu-huong-to-chuc-su-kien-moi-nhat-2019.html\/#Truyen_thong_su_kien_cung_mang_xa_hoi\" title=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\r\n<p><em><strong>T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n<\/strong> lu\u00f4n n\u1eb1m trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i quan t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i doanh nghi\u1ec7p b\u1edfi m\u1ed7i s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p trong <strong>k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch marketing<\/strong>, ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u00e0 m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng. V\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, doanh nghi\u1ec7p lu\u00f4n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/23-trung-tam-to-chuc-su-kien-chuyen-nghiep-tai-ha-noi.html\/\">\u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/wikimarketing.vn\/kinh-nghiem-chuc-su-kien-ngoai-troi.html\/\">c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c<\/a> m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 ghi l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng<strong> xu h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t<\/strong> m\u00e0 c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi.<\/em><\/p>\r\n<p>\r\n\r\n<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4399\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/ev-banner-concert-750x400-1.png\" alt=\"T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n\" width=\"851\" height=\"454\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/ev-banner-concert-750x400-1.png 750w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/ev-banner-concert-750x400-1-300x160.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 851px) 100vw, 851px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"To_chuc_su_kien_ket_hop_team-building\"><\/span><strong>T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p team-building<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Ng\u00e0y nay, thay v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n theo c\u00e1c k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i. C\u00e1c<strong>\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/cong-ty-to-chuc-su-kien-tai-da-nang.html\/\">\u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n<\/a><\/strong>\u00a0lu\u00f4n mong mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5u ch\u00fang \u0111i m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat ;v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed, teambuilding vui nh\u1ed9n. Qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tinh th\u1ea7n, phong th\u00e1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong doanh nghi\u1ec7p.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4400\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/2e3339470b344f-h3.jpg\" alt=\"T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p team-building\" width=\"851\" height=\"567\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/2e3339470b344f-h3.jpg 800w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/2e3339470b344f-h3-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/2e3339470b344f-h3-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 851px) 100vw, 851px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Theo \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi\u00a0<strong>xu h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n\u00a0<\/strong>k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p team building. Ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng l\u00ean \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho c\u00e1c tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i theo phong c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00f3m; k\u00edch th\u00edch s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 l\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n v\u1edbi doanh nghi\u1ec7p. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y. Sao cho kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfn tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c chung c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"To_chuc_su_kien_than_thien_voi_moi_truong\"><\/span><strong>T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c x\u00f3a b\u1ecf c\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian ch\u1eadt h\u1eb9p n\u01a1i ph\u1ed1 ph\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fac, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0: <em>c\u00f4ng vi\u00ean, b\u00e3i bi\u1ec3n, khu du l\u1ecbch sinh th\u00e1i, \u2026<\/em><\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4401\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/sukienngoaitroi.jpg\" alt=\"xu h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \" width=\"851\" height=\"522\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/sukienngoaitroi.jpg 864w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/sukienngoaitroi-300x184.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/sukienngoaitroi-768x471.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 851px) 100vw, 851px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><br \/>T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, th\u00edch th\u00fa v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham gia m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap cho nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng, s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111i k\u00e8m th\u00eam phong ph\u00fa<\/p>\r\n<p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/pool-party-xu-huong-mua-he.html\/\">Poor Party &#8211; Xu th\u1ebf t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n m\u1edbi cho m\u00f9a h\u00e8 s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/a><\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ung_dung_cong_nghe_hien_dai_vao_to_chuc_su_kien\"><\/span><strong>\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0o t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c linh ho\u1ea1t s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng th\u00f4ng minh tr\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, laptop s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham gia. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng\u00a0<strong>m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh LED<\/strong>\u00a0thay th\u1ebf cho c\u00e1c ph\u00f4ng xanh, m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh LCD, \u2026<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4402\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/630ent_larcencial1_20120430.jpg\" alt=\"xu h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \" width=\"851\" height=\"567\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/630ent_larcencial1_20120430.jpg 630w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/630ent_larcencial1_20120430-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 851px) 100vw, 851px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><br \/>S\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb thu v\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 nh\u1ecf. C\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u00e0ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng c\u00e0ng mang \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Truyen_thong_su_kien_cung_mang_xa_hoi\"><\/span><strong>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Nh\u1edd v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Facebook, vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n tr\u00ean Facebook v\u1edbi thu\u1eadt to\u00e1n v\u00e0 <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-quang-cao-facebook.html\/\">d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o<\/a> mang th\u00f4ng tin s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n, t\u1ea1o hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c cho quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ch\u00fang.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4403\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/MAP-2018-exhibition-banner-web.jpg\" alt=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \" width=\"851\" height=\"445\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/MAP-2018-exhibition-banner-web.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/MAP-2018-exhibition-banner-web-300x157.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/09\/MAP-2018-exhibition-banner-web-768x402.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 851px) 100vw, 851px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>S\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, trao \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00f4ng tin s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n hay c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 li\u00ean quan c\u00e0ng t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cho s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\r\n<p><em>Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng <strong>xu h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n<\/strong> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media mu\u1ed1n chia s\u1ebb cho b\u1ea1n. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t <a href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-su-kien-tai-hai-phong.html\/\">d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdn g\u00f3i<\/a> th\u00ec h\u00e3y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay v\u1edbi \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n v\u00e0 b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 nhanh ch\u00f3ng nh\u1ea5t nh\u00e9!<\/em><\/p>\r\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n lu\u00f4n n\u1eb1m trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i quan t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i doanh nghi\u1ec7p b\u1edfi m\u1ed7i s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch marketing, ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u00e0 m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng. V\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, doanh&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4406,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[94,65,84,64,66,63,26,89,88,93,91,90,92],"tags":[365,101,366],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v18.7 (Yoast SEO v19.9) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Nh\u1eefng Xu H\u01b0\u1edbng T\u1ed5 Ch\u1ee9c S\u1ef1 Ki\u1ec7n M\u1edbi Nh\u1ea5t 2019 | \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Multimedia<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n lu\u00f4n n\u1eb1m trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i quan t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i doanh nghi\u1ec7p. \u00dd t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o? Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u